# Predicting House Prices with Linear Regression

## Objective
To predict house prices using Linear Regression model.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn

## Steps Performed
- Data Cleaning
- Exploratory Data Analysis
- Feature Selection
- Model Building (Linear Regression)
- Model Evaluation

## Key Insights
- Area and number of rooms significantly affect price.
- Model shows good prediction accuracy.
- Price increases proportionally with property size.

## Conclusion
Linear Regression model successfully predicted house prices based on selected features.
